title: Saint Laurent Nano Sac De Jour
description: Saint Laurent nano Sac De Jour bag in black croc embossed leather. Featuring silver-tone hardware, dual top leather handles, accordion sides, and leather encased padlock. The open top reveals to a black leather interior. Approximate dimensions: 22m(W) x 17.5cm(H) x 10cm(D), handle drop 7.5cm, detachable leather strap drop 60cm, adjustable. Accompanied by YSL card, keys and dustbag. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned)
